  FAMOUS PEOPLE
============================================================

Name:          Confucius
Lived:         551 - -479
Nationality:   Chinese
Field:         Philosophy
Known For:     Confucianism
Contribution:  Ren, li, filial piety; still shapes East Asian society 2,500 years later
Quote:         "It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop."

Name:          Mahatma Gandhi
Lived:         1869 - 1948
Nationality:   Indian
Field:         Politics
Known For:     Non-violent independence movement
Contribution:  Led India to independence; satyagraha philosophy; influenced MLK and Mandela
Quote:         "Be the change you wish to see in the world."

Name:          Nikola Tesla
Lived:         1856 - 1943
Nationality:   Serbian-American
Field:         Engineering
Known For:     AC electricity, induction motor
Contribution:  Alternating current power systems; Tesla coil; radio foundation
Quote:         "The present is theirs; the future is mine."

